ata-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F04%2F20%2Fd629xU.jpg&h=4d4a20dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n量價齊升 前面成交一排差唔多<br />\n突然有筆大錢入黎 推郁股價<br />\n意味後面多數會升<br />\n<br />\n反之 大成交跌要小心 走人<br />\n<br />\n其他咩頭肩頂 底 macd rsi 不討論<br />\n指標愈多愈容易混淆 <br />\n化繁為簡"},{"pid":"82507a243b75fc07f81fdb93a06dcdb031a4d489","tid":1116723,"uid":246290,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T09:03:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a34bfc7193b66a73125d98b5afc1b67690d2de6","tid":1116723,"uid":246290,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T09:04:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7fef655fed4dc4b34f51cb825b32a188f2c15543","tid":1116723,"uid":246290,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T09:04:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b77cfe1b7ae06ed69481fe3ecbc0c0d53a9eac3","tid":1116723,"uid":19065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T09:58:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d73102bbb743d15af9610a488325cb1e32a3b99","tid":1116723,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T10:00:08.000Z","msg":"點睇5 仔"},{"pid":"dd267d9e49e1e2d0dcc362acde53962b93400112","tid":1116723,"uid":108814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d73102bbb743d15af9610a488325cb1e32a3b99","tid":1116723,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T10:00:08.000Z","msg":"點睇5 仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T10:06:46.000Z","msg":"恆指再上要靠佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想穩陣其實可買些少<br />\n橫盤做左個底 呢家買其實幾安全"},{"pid":"9925f25f09c6cc6af9a814938ab7bba2a566e9aa","tid":1116723,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T10:23:22.000Z","msg":"留名學野<br />\n巴打仲有冇野分享多啲？ 淨係講啲terms都可以  自己去學"},{"pid":"c11d65664988fde4cf8d17dad88310f4b8c83a89","tid":1116723,"uid":137521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0